        <num>37-7-120</num>
        <content>
          <p>It is the policy of this state that no person shall be denied care and treatment for alcoholism, drug dependency, or drug abuse nor shall services be delayed at a facility of the state or a political subdivision of the state because of inability to pay for such care and treatment.</p>
          <p>(Code 1933, ยง 88-402.3, enacted by Ga. L. 1978, p. 1856, ยง 1.)</p>
